---
// AboutSection.astro — "Who We Are" section
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3" style="color: var(--brand)">
          Who We Are
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6">
          OSU's Home for<br />
          <span class="brand-gradient-text">Competitive Gaming</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-lg">
          <p>
            The Esports Association at OSU (EAOSU) is a student-run organization dedicated to
            building a thriving competitive gaming community on campus. Whether you're a
            seasoned tournament competitor or just getting into ranked play, there's a place
            for you here.
          </p>
          <p>
            We host weekly scrimmages, inter-university tournaments, watch parties, and casual
            game nights across a wide range of titles — from shooters to MOBAs to fighting
            games. Our teams practice regularly and compete in collegiate leagues throughout
            the academic year.
          </p>
          <p>
            Beyond competition, EAOSU is a community. We're here to help you make
            connections, sharpen your skills, and have fun doing what you love.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats / Highlights -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {[
          { value: "500+", label: "Members" },
          { value: "10+", label: "Active Teams" },
          { value: "20+", label: "Titles Played" },
          { value: "2020", label: "Founded" },
        ].map(({ value, label }) => (
          <div
            class="rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-1 border border-border/60"
            style="background: var(--color-card)"
          >
            <span
              class="text-5xl font-black brand-gradient-text"
            >
              {value}
            </span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground font-medium">{label}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
